{"tid":720420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美國) 特朗普盛讚「極左」候選人","createTime":"2018-06-28T01:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T07:05:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"33ba4e70f23328934894c50ff457e48e95b5c3a9","tid":720420,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"根據新唐人報導:  「令外界驚訝的是，已經連任10個任期，來自紐約州第14區國會眾議院的民主黨團主席喬&bull;克勞利(Joe Crowley)卻在初選中出局，輸給了28歲並首次參選的社會主義者奧卡西奧-科爾特斯(Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez)。  極左勢力分走民主黨的蛋糕，美國輿論對此頗為憂心。」<br />\n<br />\n不過,  Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez雖然係極左侯選人, 但卻反被Donald Trump讚賞: Donald Trump讚賞她充滿活力 (a lot of energy).<br />\n<br />\nSource: ABC新聞記者Johnny Verhovek<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/JTHVerhovek/status/1012139061161742336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJTHVerhovek%2Fstatus%2F1012139061161742336&d=oF%2B7shHiHnXH04nVPe8eUm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3b92b8ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJTHVerhovek%2Fstatus%2F1012139061161742336&h=893b6bd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/JTHVerhovek/status/1012139061161742336</a><br />\n<br />\nJohnny Verhovek<br />\n&rlm;@JTHVerhovek<br />\n<br />\nTrump on Crowley's loss: &ldquo;Last night we had a great evening...we were winning left and right.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;One of my biggest critics&hellip;Joe Crowley, got his ass kicked. By a young woman with a lot of energy.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n6:02 PM - 27 Jun 2018"},{"pid":"8b6c8fe46b5fd59e69382697a0189c3624d0d89e","tid":720420,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"(其實有好多極左都係支持侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   )"},{"pid":"215b487e19bc63834798f1ba49c2b03a0cf9c163","tid":720420,"uid":131691,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T02:15:23.000Z","msg":"極左極右相繼上場，拉開政治光譜<br />\n玩死一班嘅所謂「中間偏左」同「中間偏右」，但係其實都係實行同一讓嘢大財團利益扯線公仔騎牆派<br />\n將政治變返做政治理